Interface IPathBezierSeed

A bezier seed defines the endpoints and control points of a bezier curve.

interface IPathBezierSeed {
    controls: IPoint[];
    end: IPoint;
    layer?: string;
    origin: IPoint;
    parentRange?: IBezierRange;
    type: string;
}
